These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: light-blue, orange, chestnut
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: bellflower, rose, daisy
1. the person who likes light-blue is the person who growsrose##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsrose##1
3. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
4. the person who growsrose is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |
| Color   | light-blue | chestnut | orange    |
| Flower     | rose    | daisy       | bellflower |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-2::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, bluemaster, oliveros
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, lemonade, mirinda
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
3. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
4. the bluemaster-smoker is the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| Cigar     | oliveros | tiparillo | bluemaster  |
| Beverage   | 7up  | lemonade  | mirinda |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, cola, coffee
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, november, august
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far right##1
3. the person drinking cola is the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |     3      |
| Beverage           | coffee | cola | soy-milk |
| Birthday   | may        | august    | november        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-4::.
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, caring, chess
The people use 3 different means of transport: car, train, ship
1. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing caring##1
2. the person playing chess is on the left or right of the person playing caring##3
3. the person driving the car is between the person playing chess and the person driving the ship##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Game   | chess | caring | mah-jongg |
| Transport     | train  | car    | ship  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-5::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: red, ebony, purple
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, project-manager, accountant
1. the accountant is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
2. the project-manager is on the left of the nurse##1
3. the accountant is on the right of the person who likes red##1
4. the person who likes red is between the person who likes ebony and the accountant##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |
| Color   | ebony | red | purple |
| Job     | project-manager   | nurse   | accountant   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-6::.
