.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-7::.
House: farmhouse, futuristic, cape-cod
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: november, january, october
1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the futuristic house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |     3      |
| House   | futuristic  | cape-cod    | farmhouse       |
| Birthday   | january | october | november |

