.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-8::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, bike, tram
House: gothic-revival, tower, futuristic
1. the person driving the scooter is the gothic-revival house##1
2. the tower house is in the middle##1
3. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
4. the person driving the bike is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |   3    |
| Transport   | tram        | bike  | scooter   |
| House       | futuristic | tower | gothic-revival |

