.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-9::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, snowmobile, van
3 different games are played: snooker, scrabble, backgammon
1. the person driving the scooter is on the left or right of the person driving the snowmobile##3
2. the person playing snooker is on the left of the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2   |    3    |
| Transport           | scooter | snowmobile | van |
| Game   | backgammon    | snooker | scrabble     |

