.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-10::.
There are 3 different nationalities: chinese, argentine, indian
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, goldfish, mouse
1. the indian is on the left or right of the owner of the chinchilla##3
2. the owner of the mouse is on the far right##1
3. the chinese is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality      | chinese | argentine    | indian      |
| Pet   | goldfish       | chinchilla | mouse |

