.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-11::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: crime, action, zombie
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, roller
1. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |      2       |       3        |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | action         | crime          |
| Transport        | bus | skateboard | roller |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-12::.
House: victorian, modern, gothic-revival
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: romance, fantasy, documentary
1. the person watching romance movies is between the victorian house and the modern house##2
2. the person watching fantasy movies is the modern house##1
3. the modern house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1
4. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the victorian house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3    |
| House      | modern    | gothic-revival    | victorian  |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | romance | documentary |

