.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-13::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, lemonade
3 different games are played: snooker, billiard, chess
1. the person playing snooker is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
3. the person playing chess is between the person playing billiard and the person playing snooker##2
4. the person playing snooker is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | mirinda | lemonade | almond-milk |
| Game           | billiard    | chess    | snooker       |

