.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-14::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: milk, sprite, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, funk
1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
3. the fan of funk is the fan of funk##1
4. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |    3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | milk   | sprite |
| Music-Genre   | folk | funk | classical |

