.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-15::.
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, cauliflower, lemon
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: volleyball, sailing, surfing
1. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person who's sport is surfing##1
3. the person eating cauliflower is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3     |
| Food           | cauliflower | lemon | cucumber |
| Sport   | sailing  | surfing    | volleyball     |

