.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-16::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, january, july
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, baccarat, prince
1. the baccarat-smoker is in the middle##1
2. the person who's birthday is in july is between the prince-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
3. the baccarat-smoker is on the right of the old-henry-smoker##1
4. the prince-smoker is the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in july##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |     3     |
| Birthday   | january | july | april |
| Cigar   | old-henry     | baccarat  | prince    |

