.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-18::.
City: new-york, liverpool, nizza
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: soul, electronic, funk
1. the person traveling to liverpool is in the middle##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the person traveling to liverpool##3
4. the fan of soul is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
5. the person traveling to liverpool is the fan of electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |       3       |
| City       | new-york | liverpool | nizza |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | electronic   | funk    |

