.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-3-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: swimming, badminton, surfing
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, zinnia, amaryllis
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |      3      |
| Sport      | surfing    | badminton | swimming         |
| Flower   | amaryllis | zinnia  | daisy |

 